      "step_index": 3,
      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "### Structural alerts relevant to hERG\n- **Cationic amine + flanking aromatics** (classic hERG pharmacophore).\n- **Piperidine + aromatic** is explicitly a known alert class.\n- Overall looks like a \u201c**cationic center connected by a short linker to multiple aromatics**\u201d architecture that often fits the hERG cavity.",
      "tool_name": null,
